Class IssuerNameSpacesEntry

java.lang.Object
com.authlete.cbor.CBORPair
com.authlete.mdoc.IssuerNameSpacesEntry
public class IssuerNameSpacesEntry extends CBORPair
An entry in the IssuerNameSpaces structure.

For details, see ISO/IEC 18013-5:2021, 8.3.2.1.2.2 Device retrieval mdoc response.

Definition

 IssuerNameSpaces = {
     + NameSpace => [ + IssuerSignedItemBytes ]
 }
Since:
1.5
